data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! Introducing a stunning home located in the highly sought-after Cedmont Neighborhood. This magnificent home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience, making it an ideal choice for those seeking a remarkable living experience. With its five bedrooms, three baths, pellet stove, fenced yard with deck and covered area, plus a detached garage, this property is truly a gem worth exploring. Nestled in the charming Cedmont Neighborhood, this home boasts a prime location that provides easy access to a wealth of amenities and attractions. Enjoy the nearby parks, schools, and shopping centers, ensuring that everything you need is just moments away. Step inside and be greeted by an inviting atmosphere that exudes warmth and sophistication. The spacious layout encompasses five well-appointed bedrooms, providing ample space for the entire family or accommodating guests with ease. There is comfort and ease with a full bathroom on each of the three levels. A standout feature of this residence is the cozy pellet stove, offering a delightful ambiance and a cost-effective heating solution during the colder months. Picture yourself curling up with a good book or hosting intimate gatherings around the warm stove, creating memories that will last a lifetime. The fenced yard provides a private oasis perfect for outdoor activities, relaxation, and entertaining. Whether you envision a tranquil retreat or a vibrant space for social gatherings, this backyard will exceed your expectations. Completing this remarkable property is a detached garage, offering secure parking and additional storage options. Enjoy the convenience of having ample space for vehicles and hobbies or transforming it into a workshop according to your needs. Immerse yourself in the timeless beauty of this home, where every detail has been thoughtfully considered. From the spacious rooms and stained glass details to the modern appliances, this residence effortlessly combines functionality and style. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this Cedmont Neighborhood home yours. Schedule a viewing today and discover the true essence of luxurious living in a vibrant and desirable community. Contact our dedicated real estate agent or visit our website for more information. Your dream home awaits!
